### Description

Schematic schema validation should match [json schema documentation](https://json-schema.org/understanding-json-schema/reference/conditionals.html). Creating a schematic with a similar schema structure as the example and passing in `{street_address: "24 Sussex Drive", country: "Canada", postal_code: "10000"}` should fail with error:
```
"Invalid: data.postal_code should match pattern \"[A-Z][0-9‚Ä¶A-Z] [0-9][A-Z][0-9]\", data should match \"else\" schema"
```

